---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="How this website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience and analyse website performance."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal">
        <p class="legal__intro">
          This website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience and to
          help analyse website performance.
        </p>

        <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files that store information about how you use
          the site. They help improve functionality and performance.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Types of Cookies Used</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Used to understand how visitors use the site (via standard analytics tools).</li>
          <li><strong>Functionality cookies:</strong> Help remember preferences such as page layout.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How Cookies Are Used</h2>
        <p>Cookies may be used to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Improve website performance</li>
          <li>Monitor traffic and usage patterns</li>
          <li>Remember visitor preferences</li>
        </ul>
        <p>No cookies are used for advertising or tracking across other websites.</p>

        <h2>4. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Most web browsers allow you to block or delete cookies through their
          settings. You can disable them at any time.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Cookie Policy, please contact:
          <a href="mailto:michael@mulhernfc.com">michael@mulhernfc.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  .legal {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal__intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .legal p {
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .legal a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold-hover);
  }

  .legal ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .legal li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .legal li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
  }
</style>
